name: fastapi_authen
description: 1. Run fastapi     - Run with uvicorn         ```shell         python -m uvicorn app.main:app --reload         ``` 2. Save requirements.txt     ```shell     pip --disable-pip-version-check list --format=freeze >requirements.txt     ´´´ 3. Install packages with pip # 4. Install packages with poetry # 5. .env data     Variables needed to configure in the environment .env file     - User is the user configured in the database administrator     - Password is the password configured in the database administrator     - Host is localhost by default, just use the service name if docker compose is used     - Port is 5432 or the configured port in the database administrator     - Name is the name of the server created
